snippet.title: Oprah 'Surprised' At Impact Of Harry & Meghan Interview
snippet.description:
After Oprah Winfrey said she's surprised at the impact her interview with Prince Harry and Meghan Markle has had, Cheryl Hickey and Graeme O'Neil discuss during ET Canada Live.
